OL,3,CSome schools which become integrated
OL,4,C'not achieving diversity targets'
OL,6,FSome Northern Ireland schools which
OL,7,Ftransform to become officially
OL,8,Fintegrated are not achieving diversity
OL,9,Ftargets, Paul Givan has said.
OL,11,FIn a written statement to the
OL,12,FAssembly, the Stormont Education
OL,13,FMinister set out his department's
OL,14,Fapproach to "reasonable numbers" in
OL,15,Fthe sector.
