OL,3,CSome schools which become integrated
OL,4,C'not achieving diversity targets'
OL,6,FMr Givan said there is a general
OL,7,Frequirement in legislation that a
OL,8,Fschool seeking to transform to
OL,9,Fintegrated status is likely to provide
OL,10,Fintegrated education to pupils of
OL,11,Fmixed backgrounds and abilities.
OL,13,FHe said his department's policy is
OL,14,Fthat a new integrated school should
OL,15,Fattract 30% of its pupils from the
OL,16,Fminority community in the area where
OL,17,Fit is situated.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
