OL,3,CSome schools which become integrated
OL,4,C'not achieving diversity targets'
OL,6,FExisting schools transforming to
OL,7,Fintegrated status should have at least
OL,8,F10% of their first-year intake drawn
OL,9,Ffrom the minority tradition, aiming to
OL,10,Fachieve at least 30% in the longer
OL,11,Fterm, he added.
OL,13,FIn his statement, Mr Givan said of the
OL,14,Fsix post-primary schools that have
OL,15,Ftransformed to integrated, one which
OL,16,Fdid so in 2022 has gone from 4%-6% in
OL,17,Fterms of minority representation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
