OL,3,CSome schools which become integrated
OL,4,C'not achieving diversity targets'
OL,6,FHe said in four of the six
OL,7,Ftransformations, one dating back as
OL,8,Ffar as 1998, the 20% minority pupils
OL,9,Fhas not yet been achieved, while one
OL,10,Fschool which transformed more than 25
OL,11,Fyears ago has not yet reached the year
OL,12,Fone target of 10% of minority
OL,13,Ftradition pupils.
OL,15,FHe added that none of the schools have
OL,16,Fcome close to the integrated school
OL,17,Faspiration of 40% Protestant pupils,
OL,18,F40% Catholic pupils and 20% other.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
