OL,6,FMr Givan said his position paper
OL,7,Fprovides "clarity and consistency for
OL,8,Fschools and communities considering
OL,9,Ftransformation".
OL,11,FHe said it also "reaffirms the
OL,12,Fimportance of balanced representation
OL,13,Ffrom both Protestant and Catholic
OL,14,Fcommunities".
