OL,6,F"This approach to 'reasonable numbers'
OL,7,Fis grounded in the founding principles
OL,8,Fof Integrated Education and supported
OL,9,Fby research, which emphasises the
OL,10,Fimportance of equal status and
OL,11,Frepresentation in fostering positive
OL,12,Fintergroup relations," he said.
OL,14,F"It ensures that Integrated Education
OL,15,Fcontinues to deliver on its founding
OL,16,Fpromise`bringing children together in
OL,17,Fa spirit of equality, respect, and
OL,18,Fshared learning."
