OL,6,F"An Integrated ethos is also
OL,7,Fparamount, as is the composition of
OL,8,FBoards of Governors.
OL,10,F"Unfortunately, the position paper
OL,11,Frefers little to this significant
OL,12,Faspect of Integrated Education,
OL,13,Finstead focusing almost solely on the
OL,14,Fpercentages/numbers of Protestants and
OL,15,FCatholic pupils alone."
