OL,4,C'not achieving diversity targets'
OL,6,FThe IEF said it recognises that
OL,7,Fincreasing minority enrolments can be
OL,8,Fa challenge for some schools, but that
OL,9,Fthe paper "fails to take into
OL,10,Fconsideration the different contexts
OL,11,Ffacing each school in terms of
OL,12,Fdemographics, locality and size".
OL,14,F"Some schools start the process having
OL,15,Fvery few, if any, children from a
OL,16,Fparticular faith," they said.
