OL,6,F"This is the reality of an education
OL,7,Fsystem where less than 2% of children
OL,8,Fenrolled in Catholic Maintained
OL,9,Fschools identify as Protestant and
OL,10,Fless than 9% of children attending a
OL,11,FControlled school identify as
OL,12,FCatholic."
OL,14,FThe IEF also criticised the paper as
OL,15,Fnot including "numerous examples where
OL,16,Ftransformation has been a resounding
OL,17,Fsuccess".
